description: AMUNDI MSCI INDIA UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI India Index in Euros, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to around 60 leading stocks on the Indian market, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI India UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
